  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201407/cc2604e0d77d40d2b6afa3897331c356.jpg\" style=\"height: 306px; width: 460px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">本节目为沪江部落一档美语发音模仿节目，每期节目选取30秒左右的慢速VOA新闻内容，主持人亲自朗读示范模仿发音，对发音要点进行讲解，并配以详细的语音语调示意图，手把手教你练就地道美音范儿！想要得到主持人专业的点评和意见吗？</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/app/menu/11885/\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" /></a><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">去沪江部落订阅本节目！</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">今日主持人：</strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em;\">cherryxyr</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.8em;\">30秒音频：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p623335\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">主</strong><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">持人模仿音频：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p623335\" title=\"点击获得更好的阅读体验\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_video.gif\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">模仿文本：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tAddie <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Alexander\" target=\"_blank\">Alexander</a> is 12 years old. She likes the bee display. Addie said the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/bumble\" target=\"_blank\">bumble</a> bee and the yellow bumble bee when they're not under the microscope look pretty much the same except that one is bigger than the other. But she said when she looked at the two insects under the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/microscope\" target=\"_blank\">microscope</a>, they were very different. 艾迪&middot;亚历山大今年12岁，她